## Impact

- **Users:** Multi-turn tool calling now works with Claude models via Copilot
- **Developers:** Diagnostic logs make tool call parsing failures immediately visible
- **System:** No breaking changes; backward-compatible with OpenAI format

## Future Considerations

- Monitor logs for unexpected `ValueKind` values (not String or Object)
- Consider extracting format detection into a reusable helper if other providers need it
- Track Copilot API changes that might introduce new format variations

